{"tid":322183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒反對 促餘下民主派議員「貨真價實」不合作","createTime":"2017-07-14T15:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T16:18:25.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be1520ce8a8a2aee53444db3bb00ef1a31dc0551","tid":322183,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"高等法院下午宣告四名議員喪失議席後，網上出現呼籲民主派議員總辭的聲音，認為目前地方直選只餘下14席，比建制派16席為少，而補選後民主派亦很大機會只會獲得17席，建制派有18席，可通過分組點票修改議事規則。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰在 Facebook 指總辭理據有三，包括總辭是捍衛港人僅存的尊嚴之舉、反對派已失去關鍵否決權，及剎停議會運作，破壞修改議事規則的條件。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒向獨媒記者表示反對總辭，他指只要建制派齊人出席仍然可以「開得成會」（立法會大會只須過半數出席，建制派擁有35席），通過惡法。他以新界東選區為例，若民主派議員總辭，將會有五席出缺，若同時進行補選，在比例代表制下將會有兩席落入建制派手中，不同於2010年五區公投，每區只有一席出缺，民主派肯定能「攞得返」。他反問是否要在這時候「跌多幾席」予建制派，這個問題需留待提出總辭的人解答。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒稱理解為何會有人提出總辭，但認為總辭的後果相當嚴重。他認為只要餘下在立法會的民主派議員有決心，進行「貨真價實」的不合作運動，相信沒有人會再提出總辭。"},{"pid":"3b9de36eb521a3493b89d0b1e153aef199fbfce8","tid":322183,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1050734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1050734&d=axJ0J6JlYliHZUBY0wTwIZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=71d9a914\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1050734&h=79f1f365\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1050734</a>"},{"pid":"80530b757ad5fe972930cd907823d8bf976f90ea","tid":322183,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:35:40.000Z","msg":"點會?<br />\n<br />\n人地不知多合作！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1330136_1_L_20170512225716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1330136_1_L_20170512225716.jpg&h=18a7beb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd227d4a9e002f7ce589652ee9c04d6d2ffc600a","tid":322183,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會?<br />\n<br />\n人地不知多合作！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1330136_1_L_20170512225716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1330136_1_L_20170512225716.jpg&h=18a7beb2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68446dc58ce2ce0de2fcac204276f60ba9c3b00b","tid":322183,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"仲講送多幾席？<br />\n就係分組點票守唔住先講總辭<br />\n比你泛民保得住地區17席 保皇咪又係想過怫就過乜<br />\n17同0有分別咩"}]}